title: Nancy, Betty, Bob, and Barry - A Celebration
description:
A musical family, the four children of Alice and Clarence Lee got together and recorded all the songs that our parents taught us to sing. They gave us the joy of music, and enriched our lives, and we tried to return their love with these songs.

Though amaturish at times, these songs were an expression of our love.

The total studio time was limited to two days (it costs a LOT of money for studio time).


Feel free to question or comment - we did the best we could at the time.

Hope you enjoy ... gonzo5440 on TPB Forum
